  "prompt": "How long does it take an iStockphoto photography contributor application to be processed?",
  "response": "The processing time for an iStockphoto photography contributor application can vary, but generally, it takes about 2 to 5 business days for the application to be reviewed. However, this timeframe can be longer during peak periods or if there are issues with the application that need to be addressed.\n\nTo expedite the process, make sure your application meets all the guidelines and requirements set by iStockphoto, such as submitting high-quality images that adhere to their content standards. If you don't hear back within the expected timeframe, you can reach out to their contributor support team for an update on your application status.",
